# .trivyignore
# CVEs accepted as residual risk - each must reference THREAT_MODEL.md
#
# Format:
#   CVE-XXXX-XXXXX  # <justification> | Risk: <level> | Residual: <R-XX>
#
# Instructions:
#   - Add a CVE here ONLY if:
#     1. No fix is available upstream
#     2. The vulnerability is not exploitable in our deployment context
#     3. It has been reviewed and approved
#   - Each entry must have a comment with justification
#
# Currently empty - distroless:nonroot has no known CRITICAL CVEs at time of writing.
# If Trivy reports a CRITICAL with no fix available, add it here with justification.
#
# Example (DO NOT uncomment without review):
# CVE-2023-XXXXX  # No fix available in distroless as of YYYY-MM-DD | Risk: CRITICAL | Residual: R-01
